<!-- About Start -->
<div class="container-xxl py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                <div class="img-border">
                    <img class="~/content/img-fluid" src="~/Content/img/WhatsApp Image 2023-12-13 at 4.43.31 PM (1).jpeg" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
                <div class="h-100">
                    <h6 class="section-title bg-white text-start  pe-3" style="color:orange">About Us</h6>
                    <h1 class="display-6 mb-4">#1  Construction Work  With <span style="color:orange">10 Years</span> Of Experience</h1>
                    <p>
                        Welcome to Jai Maa Sailani Devi Constructions, where innovation meets craftsmanship in the dynamic world of construction. With a legacy of excellence and a commitment to quality, we are your premier partner in bringing your vision to life.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">Our company is built on a foundation of expertise, reliability, and a passion for construction. We boast a team of skilled architects, engineers, project managers, and craftsmen who bring years of collective experience to the table.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4 pb-2">
                        <img class="flex-shrink-0 rounded-circle" src="~/content/img/JAIMAASAILANI.jpeg" alt="" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                        <div class="ps-4">
                            <h6>Satyam Yadav</h6>
                            <small>M.D.</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill py-3 px-5" href="~/Home/About" style="background-color:orange">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- About End -->
