<div class="container-xxl py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                <div class="h-100">
                    <h6 class="section-title bg-white text-start text-primary pe-3">Why Choose Us</h6>
                    <h1 class="display-6 mb-4">Why People Trust Us? Learn About Us!</h1>
                    <p class="mb-4">At Jai Maa Sailani Devi Constructions, we don't just construct buildings; we build legacies. Our portfolio speaks volumes about the diverse range of successful projects we've undertaken, each leaving a lasting impact on the communities they serve.</p>
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <div class="skill">
                                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
